snippet.title: Aranock Online - Black Stronghold, Ankh Amulet - failure at the last moment
snippet.description:
18th of January, 2021, Aranock Online v2.50.09

Black Stronghold, going for the Ankh Amulet. Bit of a struggle. Essentially an identical experience to Mercenaries of Astonia.
